'''Melk''' were [[Rodent/Legends|rodent]]-sized [[Reptile/Legends|reptiles]] commonly found in the [[Ocean/Legends|oceans]] of [[Zelos II]], particularly in the [[Great Zelosi Sea]]. Primarily scavengers, these creatures typically roamed in packs and while feeding did not always make a distinction between [[Death/Legends|dead]] and live prey. The scent of [[Blood/Legends|blood]] seemed to draw them toward potential meals.<ref name="Journal">{{JournalCite|13|Day of the Sepulchral Night (short story)}}</ref>

